title: "Evaluating the Comfort Experience of a Head-Mounted Display with the Delphi Methodology"
authors: "<strong>Doyeon Lee</strong>, Byeng-Hee Chang, Jiseob Park"
journal: "Journal of Internet Computing and Services"
date: 2020-12
paper_url: "https://koreascience.kr/article/JAKO202006763002729.pdf"
